ent points. Doctors were not able to fix them immediately as there were a few clots in her brain.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://aaj.tv/2014/08/pakistani-actress-nimra-khan-seriously-injured-in-a-ccar-accident/|title=Pakistani actress Nimra Khan seriously injured in a car accident|work=Aaj News|access-date=2017-03-29|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://arynews.tv/en/pakistani-celebrities-who-met-horrible-road-accidents/|title=Pakistani celebrities who met horrible road accidents!|date=2016-08-01|work=ARYNEWS|access-date=2017-03-29|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\n=== Television ===\nShe played a lead role in her debut television play Khwaab Tabeer on [[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]. She is known for her performances in Kaisi Khushi Lekar Aaya Chand on A-Plus, opposite [[Ahsan Khan (actor)|Ahsan Khan]], Rishta Anjana Sa on [[ARY Digital|Ary Digital]] and [[Choti Si Zindagi]] on Hum TV.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.hipinpakistan.com/news/1150493|title=Shehzad Sheikh is back with Choti Si Zindagi and three more projects|date=2016-08-16|work=HIP|access-date=2017-03-29|language=en}}</ref> In 2019, she had a good year as she was praised for her performances in the smash-hit drama [[Bhool (2019 TV series)|Bhool]] on [[ARY Digital]] and popular hit series Uraan on [[A-Plus TV|A-Plus]].\n\n=== Films ===\nHer debut film was [[Blind Love (2015 film)|Blind Love]] in which she played the lead role of the blind woman Sara.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/1109362/upcoming-blind-love-hit-theatres-come-eid/|title=Upcoming: \u2018Blind Love\u2019 to hit theatres come Eid - The Express Tribune|date=2016-05-24|work=The Express Tribune|access-date=2017-03-29|language=en-US}}</ref> She appeared as Hayya in [[Saya e Khuda e Zuljalal]], an action-war film about the Pakistan independence.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1196314|title=Saya-e-Khuda-e-Zuljalal is not just another war movie, say the producers|date=2015-07-25|work=DAWN.COM|access-date=2017-03-29|language=en}}</ref>\n\n== Films ==\n* ''[[Blind Love (2016 film)|Blind Love]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[Saya e Khuda e Zuljalal]]'' (2016)\n\n== Television ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Serial\n!Movies / Drama\n!Role\n!Channel\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2013\n|Chubhan\n|Drama\n|\n|[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n|-\n|Zard E Chaon\n|Drama\n|\n|[[TVOne Pakistan|TV One]]\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2014\n|Khawab Tabeer\n|Drama\n|\n|[[Pakistan Television Corporation|PTV]]\n|-\n|[[Shareek-e-Hayat]]\n|Drama\n|\n|[[Hum TV]]\n|-\n|Pehli Jumeraat\n|Drama\n|\n|[[Express Entertainment]]\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2015\n|Chhoti Si Ghalat Fehmi\n|Drama\n|\n|[[Hum TV]]\n|-\n|[[Mere Khuda]]\n|Drama\n|Saba\n|[[Hum TV]]\n|-\n|rowspan=5|2016\n|Mere Humdum\n|Drama\n|\n|[[Aaj Entertainment]]\n|-\n|[[Jab We Wed]]\n|Drama\n|Rumi\n|[[Urdu 1]]\n|-\n|Kaisi Khushi Le ke Aya Chand\n|Drama\n|\n|[[A-Plus TV|A-Plus]]\n|-\n|Rishta Anjana Sa\n|Drama\n|\n|[[Ary Digital]]\n|-\n|''[[Choti Si Zindagi]]''\n|Drama\n|Azra\n|[[Hum TV]]\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2017\n|''[[Baaghi (TV series)|Baaghi]]''\n|Drama\n|Munni\n|[[Urdu 1]]\n|-\n|''[[Alif Allah Aur Insaan]]''\n|Drama\n|Zimmal\n|[[Hum TV]]\n|-\n|''[[Meherbaan (drama)|Meherbaan]]''\n|Drama\n|Dua\n|[[A-Plus TV|A-Plus]]\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2019\n|Uraan\n|Drama\n|\n|[[A-Plus TV|A-Plus]]\n|-\n|[[Daag (TV series)|Bhool]]\n|Drama\n|Sidra\n|[[ARY Digital]]\n|-\n|Main Jeena Chahthi Hoon\n|Drama\n|Sidra\n|[[PTV Home]]\n|}\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n{{Refbegin}}\n:* [http://www.awamiweb.com/actress-nimra-khan-new-face-pakistani-showbiz-71967.html Actress Nimra Khan \u2013 A New Face in Pakistani Showbiz]\n:* [https://fashion360.pk/beautiful-and-talented-actress-nimra-khan-got-engaged/ Beautiful and Talented Actress Nimra Khan got Engaged]\n:* [http://reviewit.pk/nimra-khans-first-interview-after-her-accident/ Nimra Khan\u2019s First Interview After Her Accident]\n:* [http://he99.blogspot.com/2014/10/actress-nimra-khans-survival-journey.html Actress Nimra Khan's survival 